[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0536","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0536.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0322","title":"FreeBSD open() 函数本地任意文件写入漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 操作系统的 open() 函数存在权限检查缺陷，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞以提升的权限向任意文件执行写入操作。该漏洞影响早期版本的 FreeBSD 系统，攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限。由于漏洞利用需要本地账户，CVSS 评分仅为 2.1，危害等级较低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0322"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:08.983","remediation":"升级 FreeBSD 系统至 3.0-RELEASE 或更高版本，该版本已修复 open() 系统调用中因缺乏权限检查导致的任意文件写入问题。如无法升级，可通过 sysctl 设置 kern.securelevel=1 提高内核安全等级，限制非 root 用户对敏感文件的 open 调用，并严格管控本地用户的可信度。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6092"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0536.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0228","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0228.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0097","title":"IBM AIX FTP 客户端命令注入漏洞","description":"AIX FTP 客户端在处理来自恶意 FTP 服务器的响应时存在命令注入漏洞。攻击者通过在 FTP 协议响应中嵌入 shell 元字符（如管道符 |），当用户连接至攻击者控制的 FTP 服务器时，恶意内容被传递给 shell 执行，导致远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 操作系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，攻击者无需身份认证即可完全控制受害系统。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0097"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.750","remediation":"建议升级至 AIX 4.3.3 及以上维护版本，或安装 IBM APAR 安全补丁（IX72452 / IY07246）。如无法升级，可使用 OpenSSH sftp 替代 ftp 命令进行文件传输，或在 /usr/bin/ftp 上通过 chmod 移除不必要的执行权限以限制使用。避免使用 AIX ftp 客户端连接不可信或不受控的 FTP 服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0097"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0228.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0221","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0221.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0094","title":"IBM AIX piodmgrsu 命令本地权限提升漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 操作系统中 piodmgrsu 命令存在权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可通过利用该命令对用户组权限验证的缺陷，在未获得授权的情况下获取额外的用户组权限，从而扩大系统访问范围，执行越权操作。该漏洞影响多个 AIX 版本，攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限方可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0094"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.320","remediation":"安装 IBM 提供的对应 APAR 补丁（如 IX66020），或移除 piodmgrsu 命令的 setgid 权限（chmod g-s /usr/bin/piodmgrsu），并限制仅授权管理员可执行，防止本地用户利用此命令获取额外组权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0094"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0221.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0219","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0219.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0093","title":"IBM AIX nslookup 命令本地权限提升漏洞","description":"AIX 操作系统自带的 nslookup 命令在执行过程中未能正确清除提升的特权，导致本地普通用户可通过调用该命令获得 root 权限。攻击者只需拥有系统本地访问权限即可利用此漏洞，无需身份认证或用户交互。该漏洞影响多个 AIX 发行版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议升级 AIX 操作系统至厂商已修复的最新版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0093"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.180","remediation":"建议立即安装 IBM 针对此漏洞发布的 APAR 补丁（IX73355），将 bos.net.tcp.client 文件集更新至 4.3.2.0 或更高版本。临时缓解措施可移除 nslookup 命令的 setuid root 权限：chmod u-s /usr/bin/nslookup。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0093"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0219.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0217","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0217.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0092","title":"IBM AIX 4.2.1 portmir 本地缓冲区溢出与不安全的临时文件创建漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.2.1 系统中的 /usr/bin/portmir 命令存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞，攻击者可通过向该命令传递特制超长参数触发栈溢出，覆盖返回地址以执行任意代码；同时该命令还存在不安全的临时文件创建问题，攻击者可利用符号链接竞争条件劫持临时文件实现提权。本地攻击者在拥有普通用户权限的条件下即可利用此漏洞获得 root 权限，影响 IBM AIX 4.2.1 及更早版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0092"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-10-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.030","remediation":"立即升级至 IBM AIX 5.1 及以上受支持版本，该问题已在后续版本中得到修复。如无法升级，以 root 执行 chmod 0755 /usr/bin/portmir 去除 setuid 位，并移除其他用户执行权限：chown root:system /usr/bin/portmir；同时在 /etc/security/sysck.cfg 中移除 portmir 条目标记。临时缓解措施可将需要 portmir 功能的用户加入专用组，通过 sudo 授权最小权限使用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0092","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19306","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0092.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0092","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0092.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0092.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0092.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-673v-6c89-8w4x/GHSA-673v-6c89-8w4x.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0092.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4be848c8-03f3-452a-a9ce-ef9613324759.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0217.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0214","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0214.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0091","title":"IBM AIX writesrv 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"AIX 操作系统中的 writesrv 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向该命令提交特制的输入参数触发溢出，覆盖内存中的关键数据结构以获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 多个版本，危害等级高，利用前提是攻击者具有本地系统访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0091"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-28T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:33.873","remediation":"安装 IBM AIX APAR IX68518 补丁或升级至 AIX 4.3.3 及以上维护级别。如无法立即打补丁，可移除 writesrv 命令的 setuid root 权限执行 `chmod 0500 /usr/sbin/writesrv`，或通过文件权限控制限制非 root 用户执行该命令作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0091"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0214.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0210","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0210.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0089","title":"IBM AIX libDtSvc 库本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"AIX 操作系统中的 libDtSvc 库存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向受影响服务发送超长输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，成功利用此漏洞可获取 root 权限，实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 AIX 4.3 版本，攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限，无法远程利用，危害等级为高危。CVSS v2 评分 7.2，攻击复杂度低。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0089"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-10-28","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级至 AIX 4.3.2 及以上维护级别，或安装 IBM APAR IX45523 补丁以修复 libDtSvc 库缓冲区溢出漏洞。临时缓解措施可限制不可信用户对 CDE 组件的本地访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0089","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0089"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0210.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1431","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1431.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1261","title":"Ubisoft Rainbow Six Multiplayer 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Rainbow Six 多人游戏模式存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向游戏服务器发送超长昵称（nick）命令触发该漏洞，导致目标服务崩溃造成拒绝服务，在特定条件下可能实现任意代码执行。该漏洞影响早期版本的 Rainbow Six 游戏，攻击者无需任何身份认证即可通过网络远程利用，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1261"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:03.690","remediation":"Rainbow Six 游戏已于多年前停止官方支持，不存在补丁版本。建议立即停用 Rainbow Six Multiplayer 的在线多人对战功能，并将游戏切换为单人离线模式运行。如运营方确需保留多人服务，应在防火墙或网关层对游戏服务器端口（默认 7777-7787 UDP）实施访问控制，仅允许可信 IP 段连接，并在服务器端严格限制玩家昵称（nick）字段长度为 15 个字符以内以阻断溢出触发条件，同时升级至现代平台上的 Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six Siege 作为安全替代方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/12433","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1772","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1261.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1261","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1261.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24512263eb77d6af2cecd67bd2460f761fc94bea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1261.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rmr2-r6pv-p7gw/GHSA-rmr2-r6pv-p7gw.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87805/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1261.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1431.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1345","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1345.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1131","title":"SGI IRIX DCE secd 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"IRIX 6.4 及更早版本中 OSF 分布式计算环境（DCE）安全守护进程（secd）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向该服务提交超长的 principal、group 或 organization 字段数据触发缓冲区溢出，导致系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.4 及之前版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。厂商已发布安全补丁修复此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1131"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:47.187","remediation":"升级 SGI IRIX 至 6.5 及以上版本，或安装 SGI 官方安全补丁。如无法升级，可在 /etc/inetd.conf 中禁用 dced 服务，或使用 TCP Wrappers (hosts.deny) 限制对 DCE secd 端口的访问，仅允许信任主机连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/i-060.shtml","http://www.cert.org/vendor_bulletins/VB-97.12.opengroup","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1123","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1131.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1131","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1131.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24512263eb77d6af2cecd67bd2460f761fc94bea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1131.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-vmm5-jgw2-qm8m/GHSA-vmm5-jgw2-qm8m.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88463/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1131.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5135fc52-dd10-41de-82d5-6d8dda9e716a.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e18a803826f5de26e56a6a31273d1b83fad61ed6/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1345.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0181","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0181.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0072","title":"IBM AIX xdat 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"AIX 操作系统中的 xdat 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞向 xdat 程序发送特制的超长输入参数，触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 多个版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限才能利用，成功利用后可完全控制受影响的系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0072"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-22T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:30.907","remediation":"立即安装 IBM 为该漏洞发布的 APAR 补丁（对应 AIX 4.x 及更早版本的 xdat 缓冲区溢出修复），或升级到包含该修复的 AIX 维护级别。临时缓解措施：执行 `chmod u-s /usr/sbin/xdat` 移除 xdat 的 setuid root 权限，阻止非授权用户以 root 权限执行该程序；如业务不需要 DMI（Desktop Management Interface）子系统，可卸载相应文件集或禁用 xdat 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0072"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0181.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0169","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0169.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0068","title":"PHP PHP/FI mylog 脚本任意文件读取漏洞","description":"PHP/FI 的 mylog CGI 脚本存在路径遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过构造特制的 URL 参数，读取目标服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 PHP/FI 1.0、FI 2.0 及 FI 2.0 b10 版本，利用方式简单，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0068"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-10-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:30.230","remediation":"立即移除服务器上 PHP/FI 1.0/2.0 的 mylog/mlog CGI 脚本文件，或升级至 PHP 3.0 及以上版本，该漏洞在后继版本中已修复。如无法升级，在 Web 服务器配置中禁止对该脚本的外部访问，并将 PHP/FI 替换为受支持的 PHP 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/3396","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/713","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19553","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0068.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0068","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0068.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0068.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0068.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j2h3-fmf6-5vc4/GHSA-j2h3-fmf6-5vc4.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/php_arbitrary_file_access.nasl","https://github.com/zmerry/z-marvel.github.io/blob/581a79f0e7ceb8cdb3e444922154e004cca44bbb/vulbox/webvul/high/PHP_FI%201.0_2.0%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%BB%E6%84%8F%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E(CVE-1999-0068).html","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0068.yaml","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/9e4b769742ed57395763142c26029c2f9910f15b/sara/PLIST"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0169.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0169.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0169.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0375","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0375.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0192","title":"RedHat Linux telnetd TERMCAP 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Telnet 守护进程中的 tgetent() 函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 TERMCAP 环境变量，触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 RedHat Linux 6.0 及 Slackware Linux 4.0 等版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0192"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-10-18T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:51.540","remediation":"立即禁用 telnet 服务：编辑 /etc/inetd.conf 注释 telnet 行后重启 inetd（或执行 service telnet stop），升级到不再提供 telnetd 的现代发行版；迁移至 SSH（OpenSSH）替代远程管理。如必须保留 telnet，可安装 TCP Wrapper 配置 hosts.allow/hosts.deny 限制源 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0192","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19465","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0192.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0192.json","https://github.com/x0rz/EQGRP/blob/0c2354ff1073099b2aa417030b3167ec29d7279c/README.md","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0192","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0192.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0192.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0192.md","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0192.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0375.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0567","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0567.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0346","title":"PHP PHP/FI mlog 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0346 是 PHP 的 mlog CGI 脚本中存在的一个任意文件读取漏洞。攻击者可通过向目标服务器上该脚本发送特制的 HTTP 请求，利用参数注入的方式读取服务器上的任意敏感文件（如 /etc/passwd、配置文件等），导致信息泄露。该漏洞影响早期 PHP 版本，攻击条件低（无需认证、远程利用）。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0346"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:11.993","remediation":"升级至 PHP 3.0.17 或更高版本（已修复该 CGI 漏洞），或删除/禁用服务器上的 mlog CGI 脚本。若无法升级，请在 Web 服务器配置中禁止执行 /cgi-bin/php/fi/mlog 等路径，并设置文件系统权限限制 CGI 进程仅访问必要目录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/3397","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/713","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0346.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0346","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0346.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0346.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9fhg-rgm9-gqph/GHSA-9fhg-rgm9-gqph.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-misc.rules","https://github.com/mtesauro/owasp-wte/blob/e4c016caf67d59634f309f2a1feeed7dc9515abe/temp-projects/spikeproxy/contents/opt/owasp/spikeproxy/scan_database.db","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/P/php_arbitrary_file_access.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0346.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0567.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1413","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1413.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1224","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":128,\"inputTokens\":10678,\"outputTokens\":16,\"totalTokens\":10822}}","description":"CVE-1999-1224 是 IMAP 服务（如 IMAP 4.1 BETA 及可能其他版本）中存在的一个拒绝服务漏洞。其原理是 imapd 进程未能正确处理 SIGABRT（abort）信号，当本地用户向服务器发送特定顺序的命令组合时，会触发中止信号导致服务进程异常崩溃并生成核心转储（core dump）文件。该漏洞影响运行上述存在缺陷版本 IMAP 服务的系统。攻击条件为攻击者需具备目标系统的本地访问权限。利用方式是本地用户通过构造并发送特定命令序列诱发服务崩溃，不仅造成邮件服务不可用，而且生成的核心转储文件中可能包含敏感密码等凭据信息，存在信息泄露风险。","severity":"LOW","score":3.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1224"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:59.010","remediation":"升级到 IMAP 4.1 正式发布版（4.1 final 或更高版本），该版本已修复对 SIGABRT 信号处理不当的问题。若无法立即升级，可在服务端以非特权用户运行 imapd，并配置系统限制 core dump 文件生成（如执行 ulimit -c 0 或在 /etc/security/limits.conf 中设置 * hard core 0），同时收紧 imapd 运行目录权限，防止 core 文件泄露敏感口令信息。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87635124302928&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/349","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/1999/CVE-1999-1224.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dde4d96d7c1eff197b9a15817af615500736afa7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1224.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1224","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1224.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1224.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xgvp-66r9-6jg6/GHSA-xgvp-66r9-6jg6.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x85000/84478/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1224.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000223.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1413.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1315","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1315.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1062","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9125,\"outputTokens\":14,\"totalTokens\":10803}}","description":"HP LaserJet 打印机 JetDirect 卡配置 TCP/IP 协议时存在安全绕过漏洞。远程攻击者可直接向目标打印机的 TCP 9099 和 9100 端口发送 PostScript 文档，绕过打印过滤器执行任意打印操作或获取敏感信息。该漏洞影响配置了 JetDirect 卡的 HP LaserJet 系列打印机，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1062"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-04T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:37.620","remediation":"建议升级 HP JetDirect 固件至最新版本（建议升级至 J.60.09 或更高版本），或在打印机管理界面禁用 TCP 端口 9099 和 9100 的原始打印功能。若无法升级固件，建议在网络防火墙或打印机访问控制列表中阻断外部访问 TCP 9099 和 9100 端口，仅允许受信任打印服务器 IP 访问。同时建议启用打印机的访问控制列表（ACL）功能，限制仅授权 IP 地址可提交打印任务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602248518480&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1876","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7481e97cf7b60a5b982d99d7dad1ea61174940fb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1062.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1062","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1062.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bc48b6c04c59ceff2d71da45cd843fc1d449dc48/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1062.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vcj4-948w-5pwr/GHSA-vcj4-948w-5pwr.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/h/hp_remote_print.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1062.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87936/info.html","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_bypass.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1315.toml"}]